  "texts": [
    "SBERT captures contextual relationships within text, making it well-suited for our task, given its ability to generate embeddings that represent emotional cues such as those of fear.",
    "These embeddings served as input features for all the classification models.",
    "To address the high dimensionality of the feature space and to improve computational efficiency, we applied Principal Component Analysis (PCA) for dimensionality reduction on the training dataset.",
    "PCA transforms the data into a new coordinate system, reducing the number of total variables while retaining those that contribute most to the variance.",
    "This step was crucial for enhancing model performance by mitigating the curse of dimensionality and focusing on the most informative aspects of the data."
  ],
